#   englishwithsoheila.net    { encode zstd gzip
#                               reverse_proxy englishwithsoheila-web:8080 }
#   www.englishwithsoheila.net { redir https://englishwithsoheila.net{uri} permanent }
# and re-attach the `web-edge` network in that project's compose.
